All Implemented Interfaces:
IAdvancedStateMotor, IBlockingAdvancedStateMotor, IStateMotor, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<K,java.lang.Integer>
public class RestorePointMotor<K>
extends java.util.HashMap<K,java.lang.Integer>
implements IBlockingAdvancedStateMotor

A special motor controller that can remember certain set positions, and allow you to move to them. (Like open and close positions for a simple claw)

Author:
Benjamin Woodruff
See Also:
Motor, Serialized Form
